<!-- +++++++++++ Connection_zone +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_arm.Connection_zone">
A <b>Connection_zone</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>. 
A <b>Connection_zone</b> is an area on the surface of a design object that 
may be used to establish electrical or physical connectivity with another design object.  
A <b>Connection_zone</b> shape is defined in the shape definition of the feature that references the <b>Connection_zone</b>.  
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_arm.Connection_zone.wr:WR1">
A <b>Connection_zone</b> shall be referenced at least once.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_arm.Connection_zone.wr:IP1">
All points in a <b>Connection_zone</b> shall be topologically connected.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_arm.Connection_zone.wr:IP2">
A particular instance of <b>Connection_zone</b> shall be referenced by exactly one shape instantiation.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_arm.Connection_zone.wr:IP3">
A particular instance of <b>Connection_zone</b> shall be referenced by exactly one feature.
</ext_description>

<!-- +++++++++++ Shape_feature +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_arm.Shape_feature">
A <b>Shape_feature</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_arm.Shape_feature.connection_area">
specifies a role if the <express_ref linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone:arm:Feature_and_connection_zone_arm.Connection_zone"/> for the <b>Shape_feature</b>. The value of this attribute need not be specified.
</ext_description>
